[B]To increase faction with heretics I've found the best way to do it is not to kill the erudin guards, doing so will give the following faction adjustments +Heretics, -deepwater knights, -gate callers, -craft keepers and -crimson hands.  Instead go to Freeport docks, swim out to the beach and look for Bait Masterson or his place holder Giz Dintree.  If you are high enough level...kill these two over and over to get the follow faction adjustments: Bait Masterson +Heretics, -High Council of Erudin, -Deepwater Knights...Giz Dintree +Guards of Qeynos, +Wolves of Tunare, +Guardians of the Vale, +Carson McCabe, -Circle of Unseen Hands,-Coalition of Tradefolk, -Corrupt Qeynos Guards.  The spawn rate is about 5 min and gives you enough time to do the note to Janam/Note to Rebby quests in the sewers which helps you to raise faction with freeport militia caolition of tradesfolk 1 and 3 carson mccabe and corrupt qeynos guards.  Still trying to find an easy way to improve faction with circle of unseen hands.

